{"tid":1165440,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過最好嘅朋友鐘意咗自己","createTime":"2019-05-21T19:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T04:03:54.000Z","uid":62737,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38b19a33e10cd7275f9b35079ad1e21f8c572ff5","tid":1165440,"uid":62737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:38:12.000Z","msg":"佢係男仔嚟 我係女仔<br />\n我因為以前成日俾佢話我醜樣<br />\n所以一路都覺得同佢係可以有純友誼<br />\n但係純友誼咗四五年之後 佢先排話覺得自己好鐘意我<br />\n都拒絕過佢幾次 希望佢快啲死心<br />\n本身朋友都好少 唔想連呢個朋友都冇埋<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔鐘意男仔"},{"pid":"43f5258daafd623e26f2b9f4f8eba3c65fecb98f","tid":1165440,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:40:10.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意你啊小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200185a89b777c0375248956327a2c85c1105c6b","tid":1165440,"uid":127358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:40:22.000Z","msg":"你醜樣佢都好鐘意你  咁佢應該係真心鐘意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935ee2482503f4c537621997d12aeb89c988a047","tid":1165440,"uid":62737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43f5258daafd623e26f2b9f4f8eba3c65fecb98f","tid":1165440,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:40:10.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意你啊小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:42:36.000Z","msg":"識貨"},{"pid":"54fa44b081c05fcca9ece54d9c117790a646c2a8","tid":1165440,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:43:00.000Z","msg":"坦白同佢講"},{"pid":"dfd62ddf35f8d327e5a4b84d8caa8ca17bb2c9b5","tid":1165440,"uid":240713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:44:12.000Z","msg":"我中意咗我最好嘅朋友<br />\n但佢係外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea3d7ea45a3c38db79d020fb7d5072ab6d3f294","tid":1165440,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0